      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MOTORSPORT (7) failed to feature last start after settling well back at Geelong, but prior to that won by half a length at Shepparton (25.39) beating Kraken Tommy in a Grade 5 on May 11. Tough to beat if on-song. PAW ESTRELLA (3) is generally an honest type in the frame at 18 of 54 starts but missed the placings last time when sixth (24.77) over 435m at Sale. Solid record here winning three races. Meets a moderate line up and should run well. BLANKET GAME (2) has shown good improvement at his last two starts, finishing in the money last time when 2nd at this track over 390m. Expected to feature again. BABY GIRL PEARL (4) is worth including.",
